{
  "texts": [
    "This is an online training scheme.",
    "Since RC has access to target data during its evolution, it can adjust the output weights to prevent the predictive output data from diverging.",
    "Therefore, the online training typically yields longer prediction period and better prediction performances.",
    "RC can play important roles in the control of nonlinear dynamical systems [104] [105] [106] [107] [108] [109].",
    "In particular, in the model predictive control (MPC) framework, control actions are derived based on a predictive model of the system dynamics."
  ]
}